The paper discusses techniques for e-mail spam filtering, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The focus of the paper is on Machine Learning-based spam filters, which suggests that it could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV) since these sub-categories are closely related to the use of Machine Learning in spam filtering.
